│       └── page.tsx (Enhanced stock detail - 900+ lines)
├── lib/
│   ├── types.ts (All TypeScript interfaces - 126 lines)
│   ├── learningContent.ts (Educational content - 580+ lines)
│   ├── watchlistHelpers.ts (LocalStorage utilities - 140 lines)
│   └── aiAgent.ts (Existing - used for all agent calls)

Total Lines of Code: ~2,900+ lines of production-ready TypeScript/React

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

KEY TECHNICAL DECISIONS:

1. ALL UI in separate page files (no custom component files per requirements)
2. Components defined inline within each page
3. Uses shadcn/ui components from @/components/ui/*
4. Uses lucide-react icons (NO react-icons)
5. Uses callAIAgent() from existing /lib/aiAgent.ts
6. LocalStorage for persistence (no external databases)
7. Type-safe throughout with TypeScript interfaces
8. Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
9. Smooth animations with Tailwind animate-in utilities
10. Proper error handling and loading states

